<div class="methodology">
  <h2>Methodology</h2>
  <p>Trading fees were sourced from each broker's official fee schedule and verified against their websites as of March 2026. Where brokers offer tiered pricing, we show the standard (non-promotional) rate. Active trader rates are noted where applicable with their qualification thresholds.</p>
  <p>Currency conversion fees represent the typical spread charged on automatic CAD/USD conversions. Actual spreads may vary by trade size and market conditions. Some brokers allow manual foreign exchange via Norbert's Gambit (buying/selling an interlisted stock) to reduce FX costs — this is noted where applicable.</p>
  <p>This comparison covers the 10 most widely used self-directed brokerages in Canada. Robo-advisors, full-service wealth management, and crypto-only platforms are not included.</p>
